<!doctype html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Real Madrid - Dominasi vs Chelsea & Barcelona</title>
  <style>
    :root{--bg:#0b1220;--card:#0f1724;--accent:#d4d4d8;--primary:#ffffff;--gold:#f5c542}
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    body{margin:0;font-family:Inter,ui-sans-serif,system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,'Noto Sans','Helvetica Neue',Arial; background:linear-gradient(180deg,#071028 0%, #081028 60%);color:var(--primary);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
    header{padding:28px 6%;display:flex;gap:18px;align-items:center;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04)}
    .logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
    .crest{width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:999px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff,#efefef);display:grid;place-items:center;color:#1b1b1b;font-weight:800;box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.6)}
    .brand h1{margin:0;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:0.6px}
    .brand p{margin:0;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65)}
    main{padding:36px 6%}

    .hero{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 320px;gap:24px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:24px}
    .hero-card{background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.02),rgba(255,255,255,0.01));padding:20px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03)}
    .headline{font-size:28px;margin:0 0 6px 0}
    .sub{margin:0;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75)}

    .score-highlights{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;margin-top:12px}
    .match{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:14px;border-radius:10px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.015),transparent);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.02)}
    .teams{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:center}
    .team{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;min-width:110px}
    .team .name{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)}
    .score{font-size:32px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold)}
    .vs{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)}

    .side-card{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#081229,#061224);padding:18px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03)}
    .stat{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.03)}
    .stat:last-child{border-bottom:0}

    .matches{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:18px;margin-top:18px}
    .big-card{background:var(--card);padding:18px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03)}
    .big-card h3{margin:0 0 8px 0}

    footer{padding:18px 6%;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);font-size:13px;margin-top:28px}

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width:900px){
      .hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
      .matches{grid-template-columns:1fr}
      .side-card{order:2}
    }

    /* Small animated confetti for drama (subtle) */
    .confetti{position:absolute;left:0;right:0;top:0;height:6px;pointer-events:none;overflow:hidden}
    .confetti span{position:absolute;top:0;width:6px;height:6px;opacity:.85;border-radius:2px;animation:drop 2.6s linear infinite}
    @keyframes drop{0%{transform:translateY(-20px) rotate(0) scale(.9)}100%{transform:translateY(110vh) rotate(360deg) scale(1)}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="confetti" aria-hidden="true">
    <span style="left:8%;background:#f5c542;animation-delay:0s"></span>
    <span style="left:18%;background:#ffffff;animation-delay:.2s"></span>
    <span style="left:30%;background:#d1d1d1;animation-delay:.4s"></span>
    <span style="left:50%;background:#f5c542;animation-delay:.6s"></span>
    <span style="left:72%;background:#ffffff;animation-delay:.8s"></span>
  </div>

  <header>
    <div class="logo">
      <div class="crest">RM</div>
      <div class="brand">
        <h1>Real Madrid Fanpage</h1>
        <p>Dominasi vs Chelsea & Barcelona</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <nav style="margin-left:auto;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);font-size:14px">Live • Highlights • Statistik</nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-card">
        <h2 class="headline">Real Madrid Menggila: Dua Kemenangan Besar</h2>
        <p class="sub">Sorotan pertandingan dominan melawan Chelsea dan Barcelona — gol, momen kunci, dan catatan statistik.</p>

        <div class="score-highlights">
          <div class="match">
            <div class="teams">
              <div class="team"><div class="name">Real Madrid</div><div class="score">5</div></div>
              <div class="vs">vs</div>
              <div class="team"><div class="name">Chelsea</div><div class="score">0</div></div>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align:right;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7)">Stadium: Santiago Bernabéu<br/>Tanggal: 14 Sep 2025</div>
          </div>

          <div class="match">
            <div class="teams">
              <div class="team"><div class="name">Real Madrid</div><div class="score">4</div></div>
              <div class="vs">vs</div>
              <div class="team"><div class="name">Barcelona</div><div class="score">1</div></div>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align:right;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7)">Stadium: Camp Nou<br/>Tanggal: 18 Sep 2025</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside class="side-card">
        <h3 style="margin-top:0">Statistik Cepat</h3>
        <div class="stat"><div>Gol Total</div><div><strong>9</strong></div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div>Clean Sheets</div><div><strong>1</strong></div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div>Penguasaan Bola Rata-rata</div><div><strong>68%</strong></div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div>Tembakan ke Gawang</div><div><strong>23</strong></div></div>
        <div style="margin-top:12px;font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)">Top Scorer: Vinícius Jr. (3 gol)</div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="matches">
      <article class="big-card">
        <h3>Highlight: Madrid 5–0 Chelsea</h3>
        <p style="margin:0 0 10px 0;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)">Kombinasi serangan sayap dan pressing tinggi membuat Chelsea kewalahan. Gol cepat membuka laga dan menambah tekanan sepanjang pertandingan.</p>
        <ul style="margin:0 0 0 18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85)">
          <li>10' — Gol Vini Jr. (0–1)</li>
          <li>28' — Penalti Rodrygo (0–2)</li>
          <li>55' — Gol Benzema (0–3)</li>
          <li>78' — Gol Kroos (0–4)</li>
          <li>88' — Gol Vinícius Jr. (0–5)</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="big-card">
        <h3>Highlight: Barcelona 1–4 Madrid</h3>
        <p style="margin:0 0 10px 0;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)">El Clásico berubah menjadi milik Real Madrid lewat serangan balik dan eksekusi set pieces yang rapi.</p>
        <ul style="margin:0 0 0 18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85)">
          <li>22' — Gol Vinícius Jr. (0–1)</li>
          <li>37' — Penalti Barcelona (1–1)</li>
          <li>60' — Gol Rodrygo (1–2)</li>
          <li>72' — Gol Benzema (1–3)</li>
          <li>85' — Gol Asensio (1–4)</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-top:22px">
      <div class="hero-card">
        <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px 0">Komentar pelatih</h3>
        <p style="margin:0;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)">"Penampilan luar biasa dari seluruh tim — kerja sama, kedisiplinan, dan mentalitas kemenangan yang jelas terlihat."</p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <footer>
    Halaman statis fan-made. Untuk suntingan: salin kode ini dan simpan sebagai <code>index.html</code>.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
